You look a whole lot like my uncle.

00:27:29.902 --> 00:27:31.002
Alright, cheers.

00:27:32.202 --> 00:27:35.142
Sir, have some of this while it's hot. There you go.

00:27:35.202 --> 00:27:37.172
Thank you very much.

