I'm flying out next week, so this needs to be done right away.

00:28:28.892 --> 00:28:30.732
I'll make it worth your while.

00:28:31.192 --> 00:28:33.092
Alright, looks good!

00:28:33.362 --> 00:28:34.402
Let's go.

